<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Yesu Kwetu Ni Rafiki TZR9</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Yesu kwetu ni rafiki,
 Hwamiwa haja pia;
 Tukiomba kwa Babaye
 Maombi asikia;
 Lakini twajikosesha,
 Twajitweka vibaya;
 Kwamba tulimwomba Mungu
 Dua angesikia.

[V2]
 Una dhiki na maonjo?
 Una mashaka pia.
 Haifai kufa moyo,
 Dua atasikia
 Hakuna mwingine mwema
 Wa kutuhurumia;
 Atujua tu dhaifu;
 Maombi asikia.

[V3]
 Je, hunayo hata nguvu,
 Huwezi kuendelea,
 Ujapodharauliwa
 Ujaporushwa pia,
 Watu wange kudharau,
 Wapendao dunia,
 Hukwambata mikononi,
 Dua atasikia.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>9</hymn_number>
</song>